crowdsourced_ai_results.analysis: This code defines a Windows Scheduled Task. The task is configured to execute a specific VBScript file, `c:\users\public\videos\default_an.vbs`, using `wscript.exe` with the `/b` argument for silent execution. This execution is scheduled to occur every 5 minutes, starting from August 26, 2024, at 15:17:00, provided a network connection is available and a user is interactively logged on. The task runs with least user privileges, allows execution on battery power, and will wake the system to run. It also includes settings to restart the action up to 3 times with a 1-minute interval if the initial execution fails.
